Let's begin with the frontal lobe! It's the boss of decision-making, planning, and controlling voluntry movements. Its also where your personality lives.  #line:04a357a 
It also controls your voluntary movements through an area called the motor cortex.   #line:0cc0e23 
When you speak, you can thank a special part here called Broca’s area for helping you form words.   #line:0f54db3 
And, perhaps most importantly, the frontal lobe plays a big role in shaping your emotions, personality, and social behavior. #line:0a5040d 

Fun Fact , damage to this can completely change how a person acts or reacts to things. #line:06a3455 

